@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    ViewData["Description"] = "Read the Privacy Policy of Meet Amalfi Coast and learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.";
}

<div class="legal-page row justify-content-center py-5 mt-5">
    <div class="col-lg-9">

        <h1 class="mb-3">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Last updated: July 21, 2026</p>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>

            <p>The Data Controller responsible for processing your personal data is:</p>

            <p>
                <strong>Meet Amalfi Coast</strong><br>
                Address: [Address]<br>
                Email: <a href="mailto:[email]">[Email]</a><br>
                Phone: <a href="tel:[telefono]">+39 331 956 1421</a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>2. Types of Data Collected</h2>

            <p>While using our website, we may collect personal information voluntarily provided by users, including:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Full name</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Phone number</li>
                <li>Information submitted through contact forms</li>
                <li>Information required to book tours or transfer services</li>
                <li>Newsletter subscription details</li>
            </ul>

            <p>We may also automatically collect technical information during website browsing, including:</p>

            <ul>
                <li>IP address</li>
                <li>Browser type</li>
                <li>Operating system</li>
                <li>Date and time of access</li>
                <li>Pages visited</li>
                <li>Statistical information collected through analytics tools, where consent is required.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>3. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>

            <p>Your personal data is processed for the following purposes:</p>

            <ul>
                <li>Responding to inquiries submitted through the website;</li>
                <li>Managing bookings for our services;</li>
                <li>Sending booking confirmations and appointment reminders;</li>
                <li>Processing deposit payments through Stripe;</li>
                <li>Synchronizing bookings with Google Calendar for operational management;</li>
                <li>Sending newsletters to users who have provided their consent;</li>
                <li>Analyzing website traffic and improving website performance;</li>
                <li>Complying with applicable legal obligations.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>

            <p>We process personal data based on:</p>

            <ul>
                <li>Your consent;</li>
                <li>The performance of pre-contractual measures requested by you;</li>
                <li>Compliance with legal obligations;</li>
                <li>Our legitimate interest in ensuring the security of the website.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>5. How We Process Your Data</h2>

            <p>
                Personal data is processed using electronic and digital tools while implementing
                appropriate security measures designed to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure,
                alteration, or destruction.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>

            <p>
                Personal data is retained only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes
                for which it was collected and to comply with applicable legal obligations.
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>
                    Booking information is retained for administrative, organizational, and customer support purposes.
                    Appointments that have been completed for more than one year are automatically removed from the
                    website's records.
                </li>

                <li>
                    Newsletter subscription data is retained until the user withdraws their consent.
                </li>

                <li>
                    Information submitted through the contact form is retained only for the time necessary
                    to manage the request and any related follow-up activities.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>7. Data Sharing</h2>

            <p>Your personal data is never sold or shared with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

            <p>
                To provide our services, we rely on technology providers that process personal data solely
                on our behalf and in accordance with Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (GDPR).
            </p>

            <p>The main services we use include:</p>

            <ul>
                <li>Google Firebase Firestore for booking and newsletter management;</li>
                <li>Google Calendar for booking synchronization;</li>
                <li>Stripe for secure online payment processing;</li>
                <li>SMTP email services for sending communications;</li>
                <li>Google Analytics for website traffic analysis;</li>
                <li>Google Ads for conversion tracking and advertising campaigns.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>8. International Data Transfers</h2>

            <p>
                Some services used by this website, including Google Firebase, Google Calendar,
                Google Analytics, Google Ads, and Stripe, may involve transferring personal data
                to countries outside the European Economic Area (EEA).
            </p>

            <p>
                Such transfers are carried out in accordance with Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (GDPR)
                and are protected by appropriate safeguards required by applicable law.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>

            <p>
                You may exercise the rights granted under Articles 15–22 of the GDPR at any time, including:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Access to your personal data;</li>
                <li>Correction of inaccurate data;</li>
                <li>Deletion of your personal data;</li>
                <li>Restriction of processing;</li>
                <li>Objection to processing;</li>
                <li>Data portability;</li>
                <li>Withdrawal of consent.</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                Requests may be submitted using the contact details provided in this Privacy Policy.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>10. Right to Lodge a Complaint</h2>

            <p>
                If you believe that your personal data has been processed in violation of applicable
                data protection laws, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the competent
                Data Protection Authority.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>11. Cookies</h2>

            <p>
                This website uses essential technical cookies required for the proper functioning
                of its pages. With your consent, analytical and marketing cookies, including those
                provided by Google Analytics and Google Ads, may also be used.
            </p>

            <p>
                You may manage your cookie preferences at any time through the cookie banner
                and the Cookie Policy available on this website.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>12. Newsletter and Service Communications</h2>

            <p>
                Newsletter subscription is optional and only takes place after the user has provided
                explicit consent.
            </p>

            <p>
                Every newsletter includes an unsubscribe link, allowing users to withdraw their consent
                at any time.
            </p>

            <p>
                We also send communications strictly related to the services requested, such as booking
                confirmations and appointment reminders. These communications are not promotional in
                nature and are sent solely in connection with the services requested by the user.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-4">
            <h2>13. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

            <p>
                We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time.
                Any changes will be published on this page together with the updated revision date.
            </p>
        </section>

    </div>
</div>